{"tid":2297640,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有參展商促貿發局周三前決定取消書展","createTime":"2020-11-23T11:59:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T12:33:08.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9f37b7dce0eb5cccfb2b2f788e04d1f5945a0ca1","tid":2297640,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T11:59:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561486-20201123.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561486-20201123.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=4eD5kuUGVNxCcHpGsLYUnR1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=d2c73aab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561486-20201123.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=5779a246\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561486-20201123.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n因應新型肺炎疫情踏入第四波，一群今屆書展的參展商建議，貿發局應在本星期三前決定取消本屆書展。<br />\n<br />\n名為「2020書展關注組」的一批書展參展商表示，原定7月舉行的香港書展，當時因疫情延至12月16日續辦。他們指出，由於書籍印製、訂貨及籌備等涉多項安排，早日作最後決定會否停辦書展至為關鍵，以免重蹈7月時到最後一刻才延期的覆轍。<br />\n<br />\n關注組說，如果取消本屆書展，希望貿發局能承諾，政府撥款4000萬資助書商的費用，全數保留；不收取及退回一切額外設施的費用和電費。如因疫情而自行退出書展的參展商不用罰款。至於已支付的費用，獲全數退還等。"},{"pid":"5292adf5a474753d59ecb666b9b5284732cfca9f","tid":2297640,"uid":62314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T12:02:50.000Z","msg":"熱狗係咪又要屌人中計戴口罩搞到又要延期呀？"},{"pid":"f0bc292f76d26ea25f55b214f15cbf211c024bc5","tid":2297640,"uid":310867,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T12:07:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ApdOYE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ApdOYE.png&h=6a9b52ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"227c29f3db97b5628d3c12e3f0f42fb88adf821f","tid":2297640,"uid":7051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T12:07:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84f01aad791cce8